{"tid":2267051,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"啲美國明星真係好撚on9","createTime":"2020-11-01T18:57:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T01:33:27.000Z","uid":317059,"like":53,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"74d4cd8d0d42208a3c64a9638c1ba4acd073fca0","tid":2267051,"uid":317059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T18:57:44.000Z","msg":"呢排美國大選<br />\n啲美國明星個個懶係嘢 咩以身作則<br />\n一個二個po ig 叫人去投票（暗地裡都係叫人唔好投啊trump 要投比拜登）<br />\n<br />\n結果呢兩日Halloween 個個唔戴口罩去晒開party <br />\n啲party仲要規模唔細架喎 閒閒地都一百幾十人啦<br />\n身為明星就唔該立好個榜樣比啲fans睇啦 仲要好多fans都好後生 好容易就會比人影響架嘛<br />\n宜家美國日日差唔多10k宗確診 啲人都仲可以咁開心唔戴罩周圍玩 <br />\n<br />\n一味淨係識屌啊trump啲防疫措施做得幾差 <br />\n成班on9成日唔戴罩 <br />\n就算啊trump做得幾好都冇撚用啦 晒氣"},{"pid":"4dff7782522046b59ff071c0881fd14f77b1bc26","tid":2267051,"uid":135496,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T19:03:53.000Z","msg":"雙面偽善都唔係第一日嘅事"},{"pid":"22dd275c64fbbbe65e4e67a95b28a23295c4084a","tid":2267051,"uid":33874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T19:06:51.000Z","msg":"第一日知？"},{"pid":"7dc6b0d5379472f42e1255be06886137a841671a","tid":2267051,"uid":263150,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T19:18:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.hkgolden.media/comment/3sc1ttdm.qb1ezk55ju2.zdyytsn5baa.uyl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.hkgolden.media%2Fcomment%2F3sc1ttdm.qb1ezk55ju2.zdyytsn5baa.uyl.jpg&h=19d13b29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e13c7ce2159382a08179b16cf66110ee84f09450","tid":2267051,"uid":263150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T19:20:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/tlshaw1997/status/1322633418950221825?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftlshaw1997%2Fstatus%2F1322633418950221825%3Fs%3D21&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxf5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=c611293f\" data-ef-url=\"https://